sequenceDiagram
    participant Customer
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Backend API
    participant Stripe as Stripe Service
    participant DB as Database
    participant Seller as Seller System
    participant Logistics as Shiprocket

    Customer->>Frontend: Add items to cart
    Frontend->>Frontend: Update cart state

    Customer->>Frontend: Proceed to checkout
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/v1/payments/checkout
    Note over API: Create PaymentIntent and return clientSecret

    API->>DB: Validate products & inventory
    DB-->>API: Product data available

    API->>Stripe: Create PaymentIntent
    Stripe-->>API: clientSecret & paymentIntentId

    API->>DB: Create Order (PENDING)
    API->>DB: Create Payment (PENDING)
    DB-->>API: Order created

    API-->>Frontend: clientSecret & order details
    Frontend->>Stripe: Confirm payment using Stripe Elements

    Stripe-->>Frontend: Payment success
    Stripe->>API: Webhook: payment_intent.succeeded

    Stripe->>API: Webhook: payment_intent.succeeded
    Note over API: Handle payment success

    API->>DB: Update Payment (COMPLETED)
    API->>DB: Update Order (PAID)
    API->>DB: Update Inventory (decrement stock)
    DB-->>API: Updates complete

    API->>Seller: Process seller earnings
    Note over Seller: Calculate commission & earnings
    Seller->>DB: Create Escrow entry
    Seller->>DB: Update Seller Balance (pending)
    DB-->>API: Earnings processed

    API->>Logistics: Book shipment
    Note over Logistics: Create shipping order
    Logistics-->>API: Tracking number & shipment details

    API->>DB: Create Shipment record
    API->>DB: Update Order (PROCESSING)
    DB-->>API: Shipment created

    API->>Customer: Send order confirmation email
    API->>Seller: Send new order notification

    Logistics->>API: Tracking updates (webhook)
    API->>DB: Update Shipment status
    API->>DB: Update Order status
    Note over DB: SHIPPED → OUT_FOR_DELIVERY → DELIVERED

    API->>Seller: Release escrow after delivery window
    Note over Seller: Move funds from pending to available
    Seller->>DB: Update Escrow (RELEASED)
    Seller->>DB: Update Seller Balance (available)
    DB-->>API: Escrow released

    Seller->>API: Request payout
    API->>Seller: Execute payout
    Note over Seller: Transfer to bank account
    Seller->>DB: Update Balance (locked → paid)
    DB-->>API: Payout complete

    API->>Seller: Send payout notification
